DVD releases.
English releases.
The Region 1 DVD compilations of the "Bleach" anime are released by Viz Media. 32 DVD compilations have been released by Viz Media in the United States. A DVD collection box of the first season was released on June 10, 2008, a DVD collection box of the second season was released on August 19, 2008. and a DVD collection box of the third season was released on July 7, 2009. The series has been released in the UK by Manga Entertainment in half-season sets, then re-released into season sets.
USA Singles Release
USA Box Set Release
UK Release
Region 2 (Japan).
The 88 Region 2 DVD compilations of the "Bleach" anime are grouped by season and were released in Japan by Aniplex between February 2, 2005 and January 23, 2013.
